name: ElectroCRUD
description: MySQL CRUD application built on Electron

releases.body:
## Change log
- Update available notification, sync from github tags api

## Changelog
- Added single record view, must have primary key. infrastructure for relational views.
- create dist archive bash script

## Changelog
- Custom filters, save pre-defined filters, easy UI to build where queries
- Electron updated to version 1.2.0

## Changelog
- Process List Monitor - Live MySQL process list monitor
- Full width on launch

## Changelog
- Add Project MySQL default port, according to issue #9

## Changelog
- Closed bug #7 
- Added Search feature
- Improve table view responsibility
- Table view action buttons - added icons, on small screen text hidden

## Changelog
- Aggregate functions added to the widgets: COUNT, MAX, MIN, AVG & SUM
- Progressbar on loading
- Bugfixes
- Widgets query building refactoring
- Better MySql error handling

## Changelog
- Dev deps modules updated to new versions
- Delete view
- Bugfixes

Pre-release!

### Changelog
- Fixed delete row
- Projects search
- Electron version upgraded to 1.1.0
